embodiment 1, wherein after administering the dose of rivaroxaban, the patient has at least one of the following characteristics:
<BR><BR> (i) a geometric mean of an area under the plasma concentration-time curve (AUC) of rivaroxaban in the range of from about 80% of about 165.4 .mu.gh/L to about 125% of about 551.9 .mu.gh/L after a single dose of rivaroxaban;
<BR><BR> (ii) a geometric mean of a maximum blood plasma concentration (C.sub.max) of rivaroxaban in the range of from about 80% of 28.6 .mu.g/L to about 125% of 103.0 .mu.g/L after a single dose of rivaroxaban;
